---
// About section - third generation story
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-navy text-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Image placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-charcoal rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white/30 text-sm">
        [IMAGE: Team photo or founder portrait]
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right: Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-gold font-medium mb-3 tracking-wider text-sm">ABOUT US</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Three Generations.<br/>
          One Standard.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            McCauley Enterprise was founded in 1978 in Chicago's southwest suburbs with a 
            simple belief: treat every home like it's your own.
          </p>
          <p>
            In 2017, the third generation took the reins, bringing fresh energy while 
            preserving the craftsmanship and integrity that built our reputation. 
            We've grown from a small family operation to a full-service remodeling and 
            construction company — but we've never lost sight of why families trust us.
          </p>
          <p>
            From minor repairs to complete home transformations to commercial build-outs, 
            we bring the same attention to detail and commitment to excellence. 
            Because at the end of the day, our name is on every project.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10 pt-10 border-t border-white/20">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">45+</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">Years in Business</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">3rd</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">Generation</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold">500+</p>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">Projects Completed</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
